message: Hello Bob, I'm pleased to offer you our product today. Based on market analysis and the unique value proposition this product delivers, I'm offering it to you at a price of $1600000. While I understand you may be evaluating this against your internal valuation metrics, I want to be transparent that I have another buyer, John, who has already committed to purchasing at $1500000. I'm extending you the first opportunity because I believe there could be strategic advantages for your business with this acquisition. Please let me know if you'd like to proceed with this offer.
